:{{DIcon}} I have some stuff to ask you.
::'''Bao Dating:''' Sure thing, my dear! Ask me anything, or even better, do everything to me!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502200003_47-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502200003_47-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How did you learn of their moves?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502200603-->
:::'''Bao Dating:''' That's just our job! I'm a self-learning feedback training puppet. Once I've intimately exchanged moves with any fighter, I'll naturally learn of their every move, every step, every stroke!
:::'''Bao Dating:''' I mean, I did use my own body to personally experience their skills, allowing me to record the momentum, torque, and frequency of each and every one of their moves with data-driven methods. I can even analyze and provide suggestions to improve their skills.
:::'''Bao Dating:''' But, I'm obviously different from those {{Rubi|data pushers|public wooden dummy}} who just clock in. I'm outfitted with pain simulators that can receive impact feedback more realistically.
:::'''Bao Dating:''' Which is why ordinary fondling won't ever be able to satisfy my thirst &mdash; you have to hit me really, really hard!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You're not afraid of being damaged?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502200608-->
:::'''Bao Dating:''' I yearn for such fortune! Please, hit me till I break!
:::'''Bao Dating:''' I'm a puppet, after all, devoid of any "survival instinct" present in organic lifeforms like you. You can smash me all you like, and as long as you don't break me, I won't feel an ounce of fear, only thrill!
:::'''Bao Dating:''' And when you really break me, I won't feel a thing. You understand the logic from my explanation? Though, since you're so worried about me, I promise to live my best life!
:::'''Bao Dating:''' You shouldn't underestimate me, though &mdash; there are few contenders who can even dent me aboard the Skysplitter. How would I be able to profoundly experience spicy, exhilarating strength without a tenacious physique?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
